Nairobi, Kenya: Driver of the Ongata Rongai Matatu that killed five people along Lang&#39;ata Road in Nairobi has been arrested. Francis Mukuria a.k.a Ambulance has presented himself to the police after he was informed that officers had visited both his Nairobi homes looking for him. &nbsp;He is accused of causing death by dangerous driving following last Sunday&rsquo;s accident along Lang&#39;ata Road. He has been on the run since, and his employer had until Friday next week to produce him or face prosecution. He will appear in Kibera court this morning.